/*
 * This is our main _"landing page"_ for our Peeples help files.
 */
h2
  innerValue:Peeples

micro.widgets.file
  style:"float:right; margin-left: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
  files
    /modules/peeples/desktop.hl
      href:/peeples/

p
  innerValue:@"Peeples is the user and access management system in Phosphorus Five. It allows you to grant
or deny access to different parts of your system, to your users, according to which role your users
belong to. The <em>'Peeples'</em> module, is the module where you secure access to your system, by granting
and denying access to your users. In addition, it allows you to create and manage your users."

p
  innerValue:@"Its name is a play on words, implying <em>'people'</em>, while also implying a person who
can <em>'peep'</em> into your system."


/*
 * All files at "root" of Camphora Five help folder.
 */
desktop.help.widgets.help-index
  folder:@PEEPLES/help-files/Peeples/


